# Add one debug step once

Right after publish, add this temporary step:

```yaml
- powershell: |
    Write-Host "Checking publish output:"
    Write-Host "${{ parameters.packageLocation }}"
    if (Test-Path "${{ parameters.packageLocation }}") {
      Get-ChildItem "${{ parameters.packageLocation }}" -Recurse | Select-Object FullName
    } else {
      Write-Host "Publish folder does not exist."
    }
  displayName: 'Debug publish folder'
```

This will confirm the files are really landing where you want.

